Projects

Here are a few design and developent projects I've worked on.

ELS.edu I led team in the redesign of els.edu to create an intuitive, user-centric responsive site with best-in-class UX/UI. I also helped to lead team in the development of the redesigned site to create a seamless experience across multiple devices and fast browsing. We achieved annual lead targets by increasing student applications and enrollments after the new site was launched.
Bed Bath & Beyond and buybuy BABY I served as a lead development resource for A/B testing for both Bed Bath & Beyond and buybuy BABY in a fast-paced, high-visibility environment to boost incremental revenue. I was also utilized as UX/UI design resource and for content creation for numerous teams. My redesign of the Bed Bath & Beyond Registry page header led to an increase in Registries and in Registry purchases. Freitag Print Ads This was one of the first design projects I did several years ago as a student and it remains one of my favorites to this day for its simplicity and eye-catching visuals. I created a series of four print ads with copy that I wrote and photography provided by Freitag. The message conveyed is that "eco-friendly" and "on-trend" don't have to be mutually exclusive.
